title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 - Dec 29 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 - Dec 29 2021
description:
EIB Guest Host Michael Berry, "The Czar of Talk" from NewsRadio 740 KTRH in Houston, interviews Sen. Ted Cruz (R-TX) on the illegal flood across our southern border and how the late Sen. Harry Reid's cynical move to end the filibuster of judicial nominees backfired big time. Dr. Peter A. McCullough calls to discuss the danger of the vaccines to teens and how it compares to their very low mortality rates from covid.
